Some newbie armor quests have you combine all the non-mold ingredients in your special container, which makes a special metal plate. Then you combine that plate with the mold in a forge. I'm not sure if that's the case with your specific quest, but give your journal another look and see exactly what the instructions were that you were given.

I've found that it has to be a regular forge, and not the cultural forge. They look the same, but you can tell which you have by the label on the forge window when it opens. You want the ones that just say "forge", with no other words.

